## Use case
Implementing a slightly adjusted version of the `CupertinoDatePicker`.

## Proposal
`CupertinPicker` provides an option to set `selectionOverlay` and it would be nice if `CupertinoDatePicker` does the same as well. I would propose a builder that gives the developer the ability to create the `selectionOverlay` for every column. 
For example, if we have day, month, and year on the picker the builder would be called 3 times for every column.

```dart
CupertinoDatePicker(
  selectionOverlayBuilder: (context, index, columnCount) {
    return _MyCustomSelectionOverlay();
  }
);
```

